## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of sources up to October 2023, and some articles did not provide specific publication dates. Additionally, the findings are based on secondary data, which may not capture all nuances of the topic. Further research, including primary data collection, could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the factors influencing unethical decision-making among ethical individuals.

